description: Welcome to this stunning floor-through home in a boutique luxury elevator building. This spacious 3-bed, 2.5-bath residence features an open-concept living, dining, & kitchen area centered around a sleek, stone-wrapped gas fireplace—perfect for entertaining or relaxing at home.The Chef’s Kitchen is a standout, equipped with award-winning Metropolitan Shaker cabinetry, a 36" Sub-Zero refrigerator, 36" Wolf range, 36" professional range hood, and a large white quartz island with seating for four .Enjoy a huge sliding glass door that opens to a private 20x10 Azek deck—durable & maintenance-free. The spacious primary suite offers great closet space & an oversized en-suite bathroom with a double vanity, glass-enclosed shower with body sprays and rainfall shower head & radiant heated flooring. Two additional queen-sized bedrooms feature custom closets and share a full bath with a soaking tub and radiant heated floors. A separate laundry area and additional half bath complete this condo.
